{# Evidence drill-down for a pattern card.

  Dispatched by ``card.code`` to a per-flag renderer. Most flags fall
  through to the flat chronological table
  (``_evidence/_flat_transactions``). Four codes get custom shapes that
  match how the underlying flag should be read:

    - wash_deposit_suspected → paired deposit/withdrawal layout.
    - preloan_spike → metric panel + spike rows + pre-spike baseline.
    - acceleration_clause_triggered → normal cadence then 5–10× debit.

  Two codes have no source_transactions to drill into and render an
  explanation panel instead of nothing:

    - recent_account_opening → period date + 6-month baseline playbook.
    - payroll_absent → period + revenue context + 1099-vs-W2 playbook.

  Renders nothing when the card has no source_transactions AND no
  no-evidence renderer is registered for the code.

  Inputs:
    - card: PatternCard (from aegis.web._pattern_cards)
    - latest_transactions: list[ClassifiedTransaction]  (optional;
      used by ``preloan_spike`` for the baseline panel — without it the
      panel renders the spike rows only and notes the missing context.)
    - analysis: AnalysisRow  (optional; used by the explanation panels
      for period dates and revenue figures.)
#}
{% set _custom_evidence_codes = (
  'wash_deposit_suspected',
  'preloan_spike',
  'acceleration_clause_triggered',
) %}
{% set _explanation_codes = (
  'recent_account_opening',
  'payroll_absent',
) %}
{% if card.source_transactions or card.code in _explanation_codes %}
  <details>
    <summary>{% if card.code in _explanation_codes %}Why this flag fired — click to expand{% else %}{{ card.source_transactions|length }} contributing transaction row(s) — click to expand{% endif %}</summary>
    {% if card.code == 'wash_deposit_suspected' %}
      {% include "_evidence/_wash_deposit.html.j2" %}
    {% elif card.code == 'preloan_spike' %}
      {% include "_evidence/_preloan_spike.html.j2" %}
    {% elif card.code == 'acceleration_clause_triggered' %}
      {% include "_evidence/_acceleration.html.j2" %}
    {% elif card.code == 'recent_account_opening' %}
      {% include "_evidence/_recent_account_opening.html.j2" %}
    {% elif card.code == 'payroll_absent' %}
      {% include "_evidence/_payroll_absent.html.j2" %}
    {% else %}
      {% include "_evidence/_flat_transactions.html.j2" %}
    {% endif %}
  </details>
{% endif %}
